divs: sighting detailsi was out walking my dog. the object was view when i felt the need to look upwards to the skies above, then, by chance, i saw an object moving south to north, very fast, at what i thought to be a low altitude. my street, 13th place, is on the western side of norfolk. it was visable for only a short time, maybe 20 to 25 seconds. this wasn't the first time i have viewed ufos, just the most recent and i was excited about this. i lost sight of the object when it went behind high tree branches. i have known [name moved to additional evidence section\cms\tg] a long time, he is a mufon member, i immediatly visited at his home to report the sighting.
